member.name: M:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Assert(System.Boolean)
member.summary: Checks for a condition; if the condition is false, displays a message box that shows the call stack.

The message to send to the collection.
The detailed message to send to the collection.

member.name: M:System.Diagnostics.Debug.Assert(System.Boolean,System.String,System.String,System.Object[])
member.summary: Checks for a condition; if the condition is false, outputs two messages (simple and formatted) and displays a message box that shows the call stack.

The message to send to the collection.
The composite format string (see Remarks) to send to the collection. This message contains text intermixed with zero or more format items, which correspond to objects in the array.
